      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanically sound, the vehicle benefits from a documented rod bearing service and a reinforced rear subframe\u2014essential preventative measures for the chassis. The double VANOS system has been recently overhauled to ensure optimal variable valve timing across the rev range. Equipped with the M-Variable Differential Lock and a factory-tuned suspension, this E46 offers the balanced handling and high-revving engagement enthusiasts demand. While showing signs of honest use consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains tight and the throttle response is telepathic.",
